      "content": "Hey, I'm looking into some stuff for a project in SE Portland. Can you explain how mixed-use zoning usually applies to residential districts? specifically if we're talking about small scale commercial like a corner grocery, what are the main things to look out for regarding setbacks and building encroachment on the property line?",
